OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FThirteen men accused of conspiring
OL,7,Fwith a husband to drug and rape his
OL,8,Funconscious wife have been publicly
OL,9,Fnamed for the first time.
OL,11,FReporting restrictions protecting the
OL,12,Fidentities of the co-defendants, who
OL,13,Fcome from various parts of the UK,
OL,14,Fhave been lifted ahead of a major
OL,15,Ftrial in Manchester later this year.
OL,17,FThe husband, a man in his 60s from
OL,18,FStockport, cannot be identified in
OL,19,Forder to protect the anonymity of his
OL,20,Fwife.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
