OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FWhile the husband has already admitted
OL,7,Fto some sexual offences against his
OL,8,Fwife, he is still due to face a jury
OL,9,Fon several other counts.
OL,11,FHe has denied allegations that he
OL,12,Fdrugged his wife for sex over a 21-
OL,13,Fyear period between 2004 and 2025.
OL,15,FFurthermore, he has pleaded not guilty
OL,16,Fto charges of conspiring with other
OL,17,Fmen to drug and rape his wife between
OL,18,F2018 and 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
