CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F364A1782494314
OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FAnother defendant, Keith Fotheringham,
OL,7,F59, from Dundee, Scotland, has
OL,8,Fadmitted assault by penetration,
OL,9,Fconspiracy to rape, conspiracy to
OL,10,Fassault by penetration, and conspiracy
OL,11,Fto administer a substance with intent
OL,12,Fto stupefy or overpower.
OL,14,FFotheringham entered his pleas in
OL,15,FFebruary and will be sentenced at a
OL,16,Flater date.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
