OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FAlso on trial on 1 September are David
OL,7,FGraves, 59, of Ilkeston, Derbyshire;
OL,8,FDaniel Rayner, 42, of Whitstable,
OL,9,FKent, and Karl Lindsay, 55, of
OL,10,FTaunton, Somerset.
OL,12,FThey all deny conspiracy to rape,
OL,13,Fconspiracy to assault by penetration
OL,14,Fand conspiracy to administer a
OL,15,Fsubstance with intent.
OL,17,FGraham Brougham, 73, of Northwich,
OL,18,FCheshire, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,19,Frape, conspiracy to rape and
OL,20,Fconspiracy to assault by penetration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
