OL,6,FPhilip Wild, 58, of Stockport, Greater
OL,7,FManchester, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,8,Fattempted rape, assault by
OL,9,Fpenetration, sexual assault,
OL,10,Fconspiracy to rape and conspiracy to
OL,11,Fassault by penetration.
OL,13,FMohammed Sabir, 28, of Stockport,
OL,14,Fdenies three counts of rape,
OL,15,Fconspiracy to rape and conspiracy to
OL,16,Fassault by penetration.
OL,18,FJonathan Kirk, 43, of Stockport,
OL,19,Fdenies rape, conspiracy to rape and
OL,20,Fconspiracy to assault by penetration.
