OL,6,FSean Peers, 37, of Stockport, has
OL,7,Fpleaded not guilty to assault by
OL,8,Fpenetration and conspiracy to assault
OL,9,Fby penetration.
OL,11,FJordan Wallace, 31, of Wythenshawe,
OL,12,FManchester, has pleaded not guilty to
OL,13,Frape, attempted rape and conspiracy to
OL,14,Frape.
OL,16,FAlan Keelan, 42, of Wythenshawe, and
OL,17,FRobert Stewart, 70, of Stockport, both
OL,18,Fdeny two counts of rape and conspiracy
OL,19,Fto rape,
