OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FRichard Townsend, 37, of Heywood,
OL,7,FGreater Manchester, denies assault by
OL,8,Fpenetration and conspiracy to assault
OL,9,Fby penetration.
OL,11,FOn Monday, 22 June, the husband, who
OL,12,Fcannot be identified, changed some of
OL,13,Fhis pleas after he previously denied
OL,14,Fall 48 counts he faced on the
OL,15,Findictment involving his wife.
OL,17,FHe pleaded guilty to five counts of
OL,18,Frape, six counts of assault by
OL,19,Fpenetration and three counts of sexual
OL,20,Fassault on various dates between 2022
OL,21,Fand 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
