OL,3,CThirteen men accused of plotting with
OL,4,Chusband to drug and rape wife named
OL,6,FHe also admitted sharing intimate
OL,7,Fphotographs or film of his wife,
OL,8,Fwithout her consent, for sexual
OL,9,Fgratification.
OL,11,FHe denies 11 counts of rape, two
OL,12,Fcounts of attempted rape, seven counts
OL,13,Fof assault by penetration, four counts
OL,14,Fof sexual assault, four counts of
OL,15,Fconspiracy to rape, three counts of
OL,16,Fconspiracy to assault by penetration,
OL,17,Fone count of conspiracy to administer
OL,18,Fa substance with intent and one count
OL,19,Fof administering a substance with
OL,20,Fintent.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
